# Hooras Project Skills

When working on UI, design system, or frontend implementation tasks, read the relevant skill files from `skills/**/SKILL.md` before making changes.

Available skills are listed in `skills/README.md`.

## UI Theming Rules

- Prefer semantic Tailwind classes (`bg-card`, `text-foreground`, `border-border`, `bg-muted`, `bg-overlay`) in components
- Brand aliases (`bg-cloud`, `text-ink-navy`, etc.) are valid but semantic classes are preferred for new code
- Never use `bg-black/*` overlays or hardcoded hex in component `className` strings
- Verify new UI in both light and dark mode before completing the task
